%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20recipe%20ingredients%2C%20including%20chicken%20breasts%2C%20panko%2C%20olive%20oil%2C%20whisked%20eggs%2C%20salt%2C%20and%20seasonings%20organized%20on%20the%20writer's%20kitchen%20counter.%20Stanley%20Tucci's%20book%2C%20a%20rolling%20pin%2C%20parchment%20paper%2C%20and%20a%20cutting%20board%20are%20also%20in%20frame.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6840a8e69b2a601d01b25252%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20ingredients%20mentioned%20in%20the%20recipe%2C%20I%20gathered%20smoked%20paprika%20and%20garlic%20powder%2C%20too.%3Cp%3EMyrna%20Aguilar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20start%2C%20I%20gathered%20a%20few%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstanley-tucci-cacio-e-pepe-recipe-searching-for-italy-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esimple%20ingredients%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20four%20chicken%20breasts%2C%20two%20eggs%2C%20two%20cups%20of%20panko%20(the%20recipe%20called%20for%20plain%20breadcrumbs)%2C%20%C2%BD%20cup%20of%20olive%20oil%2C%20and%20salt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20collected%20two%20pieces%20of%20parchment%20paper%2C%20a%20cutting%20board%2C%20and%20a%20rolling%20pin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20started%20by%20slicing%20the%20chicken%20breasts.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224574%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20chicken%20breasts%20sliced%20in%20half.%20The%20chicken%20breasts%20are%20laying%20on%20a%20cutting%20board%20covered%20in%20parchment%20paper.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6840a997c19ab3675c10a913%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223431%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20sliced%20each%20of%20the%20chicken%20breasts%20in%20half.%3Cp%3EMyrna%20Aguilar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20I%20sliced%20each%20of%20the%20chicken%20breasts%20lengthwise.%20Then%2C%20I%20placed%20them%20on%20a%20cutting