0%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20CEO%20of%20a%20major%20AI%20startup%20has%20dismissed%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmarketing%20move.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAGI%20is%20broadly%20used%20to%20describe%20a%20system%20that%20could%20perform%20any%20task%20that%20a%20human%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20during%20a%20fireside%20chat%20at%20London%20Tech%20Week%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistral-ai-assistant-le-chat-consumer-enterprise-arthur-mensch-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EArthur%20Mensch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20CEO%20of%20French%20startup%20Mistral%2C%20said%20that%20AGI%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20super%20well%20defined.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20moving%20target%20by%20definition%2C%26quot%3B%20Mensch%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20move%20from%20AI%20to%20AGI%20at%20some%20point%2C%20but%20that's%20a%20marketing%20move.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20Sam%20Altman%20has%20said%20that%20AGI%20could%20come%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fagi-predictions-sam-altman-dario-amodei-geoffrey-hinton-demis-hassabis-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20soon%20as%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20Google%20DeepMind's%20Demis%20Hassabis%20predicts%20it'll%20arrive%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mistral%20CEO%2C%20known%20for%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistrals-ceo-said-obsession-with-agi-about-creating-god-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAGI%20scepticism%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20progress%20should%20instead%20be%20measured%20by%20looking%20at%20%26quot%3Bthe%20length%20of%20the%20agent%20execution%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20means%20how%20long%20an%20AI%20agent%20can%20perform%20tasks%20before%20it%20runs%20into%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20number%20of%20tasks%20that%20you%20can%20do%20within%20an%20enterprise%2C%20or%20as%20a%20user%20using%20generative%20AI%20syst