F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68472bf6f748d8c055f3533d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221014%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEvercore%20ISI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESmall%20caps%2C%20initially%20perceived%20as%20a%20clear%20winner%20of%20the%20Trump%20trade%20following%20the%20election%2C%20have%20emerged%20as%20the%20biggest%20losers%20of%20the%20trade%20war.%20With%20tariff%20concerns%20top-of-mind%2C%20investors%20are%20viewing%20small%20caps%20as%20%26quot%3Bprice%20takers%2C%20not%20price%20makers%2C%26quot%3B%20extra%20vulnerable%20to%20inflation%20and%20supply%20chain%20disruptions%2C%20a%20note%20by%20Evercore%20ISI%20senior%20managing%20direction%2C%20Julian%20Emanuel%2C%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20the%20optimists%2C%20once%20you%20hit%20rock%20bottom%2C%20the%20only%20direction%20to%20go%20is%20up.%20In%20the%20eyes%20of%20Evercore%2C%20small%20caps%20have%20become%20%26quot%3Bso%20bad%2C%20they're%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22589f1225-712e-4485-bdfe-4b040e7b7533%5C%22%3EJune%20outperformance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJune%20has%20historically%20been%20a%20strong%20month%20for%20small%20caps%2C%20as%20the%20FTSE%20Russell%20rebalances%20its%20indexes%20and%20adds%20or%20removes%20stocks%20based%20on%20market%20cap%20criteria.%20This%20leads%20to%20a%20surge%20of%20trading%20activity%20that%20can%20boost%20stock%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20effect%20is%20particularly%20prominent%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20outsized%20underperformance.%20In%20the%20five%20other%20instances%20of%20disappointing%20January%20to%20May%20performance%2C%20small%20caps%20exhibited%20strong%20seasonal%20reversion%20during%20the%20month%20of%20June%2C%20outperforming%20large%20caps%20by%20an%20average%20of%204.1%25%2C%20Evercore%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20believes%20the%20market%20has%20moved%20past%20the%20point%20of%20peak%20tariff%20uncertainty%2C%20which%20could%20further%20boost%20the%20sector's%20performance%20in%20June.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20catalysts%20for%20a%20small-cap%20resurgence%20as%20well.%20Amy%20Zhang%2C%20a%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20investment%20management%20firm%20Alger%2C%20pointed%20to%20cheap%20valuations%20and%20the%20potential%20for%20rate%20cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmall%20caps%20have%20historically%20traded%20at%20a%2027%25%20premium%20relative%20to%20large%20caps%20due%20to%20their%20higher%20growth%20expectations%2C%20but%20on%20a%20forward-looking%20basis%2C%20the%20Russell%202000%20is%20currently%20only%20trading%20at%20a%2011%25%20premium%20to%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%20This%20allows%20investors%20to%20get%20exposure%20to%20small%20caps%20at%20a%20steep%20discount%20relative%20to%20history%2C%20especially%20as%20fundamentals%20and%20the%20overall%20economic%20environment%20improve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheap%20valuations%20make%20small%20caps%20appealing%20takeover%20targets%2C%20and%20a%20pickup%20in%20M%26amp%3BA%20activity%20could%20help%20lift%20the%20group%2C%20Zhang%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20As%20large%20companies%20look%20to%20boost%20growth%20through%20acquisitions%2C%20smaller%20firms%20become%20prime%20candidates.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20healthcare%20sector%2C%20the%20largest%20component%20of%20the%20Russell%202000%2C%20tends%20to%20benefit%20the%20most%20from%20increased%20dealmaking%2C%20according%20to%20Bank%20of%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Emanuel%20and%20Zhang%20believe%20lower%20rates%2C%20which%20help%20smaller%20companies%20with%20higher%20levels%20of%20debt%20on%20their%20balance%20sheets%2C%20could%20be%20coming%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20it's%20data%20dependent%2C%20they%20run%20the%20risk%20of%20being%20too%20late%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhang%20said%20of%20the%20Fed%20cutting%20rates.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20could%20be%20the%20case%2C%20like%20last%20year%20Q4%2C%20where%20the%20Fed%20may%20be%20in%20a%20position%20again%20to%20pivot%20to%2050%20basis%20points%20of%20cu