s%20like%20Kachi%20Haldi%20ki%20Sabji%2C%20Kuga%20Roti%2C%20and%20Makhaniya%20Lassi%2C%20winning%20hearts%20(and%20taste%20buds)%20from%20judges%20and%20chefs%20from%20across%20the%20world.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20no%20formal%20training%2C%20but%20I%20had%20the%20flavours%20of%20my%20culture%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20was%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELaunching%20%E2%80%98Sidhi%20Marwari%E2%80%99%3A%20A%20brand%20born%20of%20belief%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20MasterChef%2C%20Kaushalya%20realised%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F411753%2Fmadhuras-recipe-maharashtrian-cuisine-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimportance%20of%20having%20her%20platform%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20not%20just%20a%20social%20media%20page%2C%20but%20something%20she%20could%20build%20on%20her%20terms.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20TikTok%20was%20banned%20in%20India%2C%20I%20lost%2015%20lakh%20subscribers%20and%20the%20revenue%20that%20was%20generated%20out%20of%20the%20videos%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Kaushalya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20that%20my%20earning%20resource%20is%20via%20social%20media%20platforms%20like%20YouTube%2C%20Instagram%20or%20Facebook.%20If%20the%20platform%20is%20no%20longer%20there%2C%20what%20will%20I%20do%20for%20money%3F%E2%80%9D%20Kaushalya%20asked%20herself.%20This%20gave%20birth%20to%20%E2%80%98Sidhi%20Marwari%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20brand%20rooted%20in%20purity%20and%20tradition%20in%20March%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20came%20from%20a%20simple%20problem%3A%20her%20relatives%20abroad%20often%20complained%20that%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20the%20same%20flavour%20in%20Indian%20food%20made%20with%20foreign%20spices%20and%20oils.%20She%20visited%20factories%20and%20found%20poor%20hygiene%2C%20artificial%20colours%2C%20and%20shortcuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-inst