20pushed%20Dimum%20to%20focus%20more%20reviving%20such%20lost%20millets%20and%20vegetables.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20took%20some%20of%20my%20products%20there%20and%20it%20was%20quite%20interesting%20to%20across%20people%20from%20different%20ethnicities%20coming%20together%20with%20different%20ideas%20It%20was%20a%20big%20exposure%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20to%20her%20surprise%2C%20people%20were%20genuinely%20curious%20about%20her%20millet.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20carried%20two%20packets%20of%20the%20millet%20and%20they%20bought%20both%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20Dimum%20is%20also%20in%20touch%20with%20a%20fellow%20delegate%20from%20the%20expo%20who%20is%20interested%20in%20procuring%20more%20of%20the%20revived%20millet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20joy%20of%20reviving%20lost%20foods%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20just%20two%20years%2C%20Gepo%20Aali%20has%20garnered%20around%20150%20loyal%20customers%20from%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%E2%80%94%20a%20small%20but%20meaningful%20community%20that%20believes%20in%20Dimum%E2%80%99s%20vision.%20While%20revenue%20has%20been%20modest%2C%20reflecting%20the%20challenges%20of%20scaling%20a%20grassroots%20food%20venture%20in%20a%20remote%20region%2C%20Dimum%20remains%20undeterred.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20focus%20has%20never%20been%20on%20rapid%20growth%20or%20profit%20margins.%20Instead%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20rooted%20in%20steady%20and%20sustainable%20impact%20%E2%80%94%20building%20seed%20banks%2C%20empowering%20women%20through%20financial%20models%20like%20ROCA%20(Rotating%20Savings%20and%20Credit%20Association)%2C%20and%20preserving%20indigenous%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20her%20goals%20are%20ambitious%20yet%20deeply%20connected%20with%20community%20care.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20look%20for%20more%20such%20foods%20and%20revive%20them%20effectively%2C%20bring%20them%20to%20