0produce%20over%2020%2C000%20bulbs%20in%20the%20same%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20proudly.%20The%20method%20also%20helped%20the%20farmer%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F297512%2Findian-farmers-agroforestry-climate-change-solution-agriculture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincrease%20his%20income%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CMicrogreens%20farming%20allowed%20us%20to%20diversify%2C%20and%20now%20we%20are%20producing%20different%20seeds%20like%20cabbage%20and%20radish%20for%20Greenu%2C%20which%20has%20opened%20up%20a%20new%20stream%20of%20income%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20his%20training%20initiative%2C%20the%2046-year-old%20has%20taught%20over%20300%20farmers%20how%20to%20use%20minimal%20space%20to%20grow%20these%20high-value%20crops%2C%20helping%20them%20earn%20more%20with%20fewer%20resources.%20He%20also%20came%20across%20the%20incubation%20centre%20in%20Hisar%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20RKVY%20Raftaar%20scheme.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20business%20received%20support%20and%20funding%20through%20the%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETiny%20greens%2C%20big%20impact%3A%20How%20Greenu%20expanded%20to%20growing%20over%2075%20varieties%20of%20microgreens%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Greenu%20entrepreneur%20believes%20that%20the%20beauty%20of%20microgreens%20farming%20lies%20in%20its%20simplicity%20and%20efficiency.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20my%20venture%20by%20selecting%20high-quality%20and%20non%20genetically%20modified%20(non-GMO)%20seeds.%20I%20source%20mine%20from%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendras%20(KVK)%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20they%20are%20organic%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mohit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20seeds%20are%20sown%20in%20sterilised%20growing%20media%2C%20like%20cocopeat%20or%20coco%20coir%2C%20in%20trays.%20The%20microgreens%20are%20watered%20with%20a%20minimal%20amount%20of%20just%2030%2