-Feature-image-2025-06-04T172837.946_11zon-1749104214-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T172837.946_11zon-1749104214-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T172837.946_11zon-1749104214-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-444554%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20mangrove%20awareness%20programme%20also%20helps%20to%20educate%20citizens%20about%20the%20need%20to%20protect%20mangroves.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20done%20quizzes%2C%20film%20screenings%2C%20school%20debates%2C%20and%20even%20a%20first-of-its-kind%20mobile%20app%20%E2%80%94%20all%20designed%20to%20make%20mangroves%20relatable%2C%E2%80%9D%20Karkhanis%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Plural%20Biodiversity%20app%20helps%20users%20identify%20mangroves%2C%20their%20threats%2C%20and%20their%20conservation%20value.%20Available%20in%2010%20Indian%20coastal%20languages%20and%20three%20global%20ones%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20now%20used%20across%20diverse%20states%20and%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20these%20tools%20proved%20vital%20in%20keeping%20engagement%20alive%2C%20even%20when%20the%20forest%20was%20off-limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20it%20takes%20to%20protect%20a%20forest%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20city%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20achieved%20success%20is%20highly%20commendable%2C%20the%20journey%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20without%20hurdles%2C%20many%20of%20them%20invisible%20at%20first%20glance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20major%20challenge%20is%20solid%20waste.%20At%20the%20intersection%20of%20land%20and%20water%2C%20mangroves%20naturally%20trap%20debris%2C%20but%20they%E2%80%99re%20now%20inundated%20with%20garbage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%